### Registrar
POST http://localhost:3000/auth/registrar
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "nome": "Eduardo",
    "email": "eduardo@email.com",
    "senha": "senha123"
}

### Login
POST http://localhost:3000/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "email": "eduardo@email.com",
    "senha": "senha123"
}

